能係佢地一份子，除非佢肯出黎澄清佢係全面反對國安法同埋唔會鎅票。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對策：</span></span></strong><br />\n我地要全面杯葛佢地嘅成員，唔可以再幫佢地增加曝光率，譬如唔可以俾佢哋上喱show同埋100毛等等嘅媒體，同埋我地要不斷強調，尤其係向立場唔夠堅定嘅老一輩人強調，同共產黨談判就等如與虎謀皮，佢地句句都係大話，你點同佢談判？只有打倒共產黨，先係我地嘅希望。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rP0qPrg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrP0qPrg.jpg&h=c1df8bcf&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbjK4ZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnbjK4ZC.jpg&h=6a2d3702&s={SIZE}\" /> 屌你喇 民主黨兩大元老都係咁講<br />\n咁佢地係咪同袁彌昌講既野一撚樣呀 <br />\n打壓素人 夠哂民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QuTjTTu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQuTjTTu.jpg&h=be9657d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:56:13.000Z","msg":"立場姐姐出黎俾人打完一獲就唔撚做記者<br />\n走出黎選 係咪劇本呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQuTjTTu.jpg&amp;h=be9657d7&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"3ab6d9ab5fc96518b737d77d0a157e0bba4d380c","tid":2074190,"uid":156592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d40b4752c016f1c533242ec368866774972c7c5d","tid":2074190,"uid":114014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:52:39.000Z","msg":"鬼黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:56:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢個人相當有嫌疑"},{"pid":"3ab00b39c1705954fd18629e5e9fc85e6a10c108","tid":2074190,"uid":237428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"push 7/10"},{"pid":"f0cc0fa9af741e7f14ae308a5ebe9b7fc7324ee5","tid":2074190,"uid":237428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:57:10.000Z","msg":"push 8/10"},{"pid":"660ebf3043a4b927642e